@Node Main "RxMUI - Register Class"


Register class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "GroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The register class is used to create a group object that
  contains children not all visible at the same time.

  Only the children in the active page are visible.

  You must pass in Titles the names of the pages separated by | .

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}ActivePage@{fg text}
  N ISGN

  @{fg shine}RegisterFrame@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}Titles@{fg text}
  S I IND

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode

